Property Type Description <code>data_refs_to</code> <code>list[Data \| AddressT]</code> Data objects or addresses that access this member <code>type_refs_to</code> <code>list[TypeReference]</code> Types/members that reference this member (incoming) <pre><code>for struct in prog.structures:
